name: Crispy Spring Rolls
description: A deep-fried Liyue snack. Shredded meat and vegetables are wrapped in a thin pancake, rolled into a tube, and then fried until golden. Crunchy on the outside, smooth on the inside, these little delicacies are cherished by old and young alike.

suspicious.name: Suspicious Crispy Spring Rolls
suspicious.description: A deep-fried Liyue snack. The crust was supposed to be crisp, but somehow it ended up soft and soggy â€” how strange... Wait, could this be the oil paper used to wrap the food...?
suspicious.effect: Increases all party members' DEF by 165 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).

delicious.name: Delicious Crispy Spring Rolls
delicious.description: A deep-fried Liyue snack. With a crisp crack, the juicy filling bursts forth as you bite. Beneath the golden, flaky shell are not only layers of flavor, but the vibrant, bustling spirit of Liyue itself.
delicious.effect: Increases all party members' DEF by 235 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).

special.name: Flavor of Spring
special.description: Zibai's specialty. Its color gleams like golden amber, reminiscent of her eyes. Its aroma is as familiar as a simple spring roll, yet each crisp bite reveals an unexpected resilience... Could this be a secret recipe from ancient Lang-Gan?
special.effect: Increases all party members' DEF by 282 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
